data.description: DC TOPA Free!   excellent opportunity for owner occupant or future development! Fully Vacant 4 unit in sought after Brookland/Turkey Thicket.     Sentri-Lock on left handrail contains front door code.    All 4 apartments are open- please do not lock the front apartment doors!    If you open a rear door or steel gate, please lock these when exiting!! Both second floor apartments #3 & #4 are central AC in attic above.   #1 & #2 use window units for AC. Wash Gas just completed a full gas line upgrade, removing 4 meters from the hallway to the exterior front wall.   Yard restoration to be completed by Wash Gas vendor! Please be aware of motion detectors in all 4 apartments and avoid touching these monitors. See Docs for Disclosures, all contracts require 1031 Exchange Language and consent from purchaser to complete a 1031 Tax exchange. Generally everything in the building is in operating condition, 2 have Pepco power on, 2 are turned off! if you show during daylight hours no flashlight is necessary. 3918 is directly adjacent to the Turkey Thicket Recreation Center with all its benefits.  Front Mansard shingle roofing is approx 5 years old, roll roofing is a modified bitumen product with reflective paint applied to reduce heat gain!
